'''珊瑚岛上的死光'''（Death-Ray On The Coral Island）是中国在1980年拍摄的电影，<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://movie.mtime.com/46495/|title=珊瑚岛上的死光 Death-Pay On The Coral Island(1980)|date=|publisher=时光网|accessdate=2016-03-26|language=zh-cn|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312061509/http://movie.mtime.com/46495/|archive-date=2016-03-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>讲述了科学家赵谦教授制作高效原子电池，决定带回祖国的故事。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://mt.sohu.com/20150611/n414808183.shtml|title=珊瑚岛上的死光|language=zh-cn|publisher=搜狐|author=|date=|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406091542/http://mt.sohu.com/20150611/n414808183.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>原作是[[童恩正|童恩正]]的作品《珊瑚岛上的死光》。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/book/2009-06/03/content_11479963_3.htm|title=本土经典：60年60部原创儿童文学作品|language=zh-cn|publisher=新华网|author=|date=|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2009-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090709165054/http://news.xinhuanet.com/book/2009-06/03/content_11479963_3.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>本片是中华人民共和国文革結束後的第一部科幻片。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://ent.southcn.com/zhuanti2/film100/films/200509200750.htm |title = 《珊瑚岛上的死光》：科幻片的灵光乍现 |author =  |date = 2005-03-23 |publisher = 南方网 |language = zh-cn |accessdate = 2018-05-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180505135549/http://ent.southcn.com/zhuanti2/film100/films/200509200750.htm |archive-date = 2018-05-05 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>

